A highly-functional, responsive, and secured applications based on Flutter framework.

Flutter App Development

With the ability to create enthralling native apps from one code base, Flutter is quickly becoming popular for rapid growth, descriptive & versatile UI.

This unrivaled and highly stable mobile UI architecture enables the development of top-quality native frameworks on cross platforms in a small-time.

At Sahajanand Infotech, we have a team of technology experts, working since its launch in Flutter mobile apps development with excellent knowledge.

Sahajanand Infotech is among the leading technology companies for online and mobile apps, our developer is providing next generation app development services.

Using a single code base Flutter works on both Android and iOS platforms. Our developer team is exercising every new technology.

why choose Flutter?

Flutter doesn't need a JavaScript bridge to access OEM widgets that promises better native functions than other frameworks.

Migration and repurpose are achievable with Flutter code. This allows applications to be released concurrently for iOS & Android.

Flutter uses the reactive architecture of programming. This makes it easy for developers not to manually update the UI.

Flutter is a full SDK with its tools and libraries. Flutter apps do not have to rely on third-party libraries to improve their functionality.

Flutter uses DART, i.e. Google's programming language, which operates on object-oriented programming concepts.

Flutter App Development Service Include

Being cross-platform, the same code can be used for both android and ios app development. As a result, it takes less time for the developers and generates more business opportunities for organizations. On both platforms, the app can be launched simultaneously. That means applications built on flutter can function on the google platform and apple impeccably.

  • Expertise in developing simple and complex apps within the best turnaround times
  • Flutter apps are developed with tailored designs to match and enhance the brand value.
  • We develop exceptional applications infused with excellence in performance.
  • Our designs and development frameworks are unique hence delivering out-of-box solutions.
  • We develop secure and scalable ios applications to maintain integrity.
  • Platform channel data type support and codecs

Flutter App Development Process

Understanding The Project

We gather requirements, discuss the idea, brainstorm upon it and clarify all doubts regarding the project in advance.

Wireframing And Planning

Wireframing, prototyping, and feasibility analysis is done before proceeding to the design or development phase.

Graphic And UI Designing

Visual components & plans, like design strategy, psds and screens are crafted at the next step of the project development process.

Development And Optimization

Our developers create functional elements, algorithms, and other backend modules while integrating them with ui at this step.

Quality And Extension

Required changes are made, quality assurance is performed and security audit is done once the first draft is ready.

First Draft To Final Delivery

The first draft of the project is shown to the client. Once requirement changes are made and approved, we launch the project.
